<pb ed="F" id="F28.1076.0604a" n="0604a"/>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><juan fun="open" n="1"><jhead>發菩提心戒一本</jhead></juan>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a02"/><div1><p id="pF28p0604a0201">夫菩提心戒者為修六度万行之泉源是
<lb ed="F" n="0604a03"/>證三身佛果菩提之根本功最甚深理
<lb ed="F" n="0604a04"/>難思議是以三世諸佛同說三世菩薩同
<lb ed="F" n="0604a05"/>學故經云戒如明日月亦如瓔珞珠微塵
<lb ed="F" n="0604a06"/>菩薩眾由是成正覺。</p><p id="pF28p0604a0609" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">念三寶六師佛菩薩念梵釋四王金剛天</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a07"/><p id="pF28p0604a0701">將釋戒文分為八段第一奉請賢聖第二
<lb ed="F" n="0604a08"/>想陳妙供第三懺悔罪&CB07703;第四受三歸依
<lb ed="F" n="0604a09"/>戒第五翻邪歸正第六正受菩提心戒第
<lb ed="F" n="0604a10"/>七遣相第八普皆迴向八段不同。</p><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604a1014">且初第
<lb ed="F" n="0604a11"/>一奉請賢聖</p><p id="pF28p0604a1106" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">人各整衣&CI0004;合掌聞舉弟子某甲等處隨言後說</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a12"/><lg id="lgF28p0604a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">弟子某甲等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">稽首皈命禮</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">遍虛空法界</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">十方諸如&CB08074;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">瑜伽&CB01628;持教</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸大菩薩眾</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">及禮菩提心</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">能滿福智聚</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">令得無上覺</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">是故志心禮</l></lg><p id="pF28p0604a1506" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">三說　念無盡三寶願降臨</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a16"/><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604a1601">第二想陳妙供</p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a17"/><lg id="lgF28p0604a1701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">弟子某甲等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">十方一切剎</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">所<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">有</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app>諸供養</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a18"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">花鬘塗香等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">飲食<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">幢</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">憧</rdg></app>幡&CB02649;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">誠心普奉獻</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a19"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸佛諸法藏</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸大菩薩眾</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">及諸賢聖等</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a20"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">我今志心禮</l></lg><p id="pF28p0604a2006" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">三說　念供養無盡諸三寶</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a21"/><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604a2101">第三懺悔罪&CB07703;</p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a22"/><lg id="lgF28p0604a2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">弟子某甲等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">從無始<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB08074;</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">輪迴生死</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a23"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">乃至今日</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">所造眾罪</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">無量無邊</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a24"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">不自覺知</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">自作教他</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">見作隨喜</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a25"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">我今懺悔</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不復更造</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">唯願諸佛</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a26"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">慈悲攝受</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">令我罪障</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">速得消滅</l></lg>
<lb ed="F" n="0604a27"/><p id="pF28p0604a2701" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">念普賢菩薩懺悔師</note></p>
<pb ed="F" id="F28.1076.0604b" n="0604b"/>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b01"/><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604b0101"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">第</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">弟</rdg></app>四受三歸依戒</p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b02"/><lg id="lgF28p0604b0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">弟子某甲等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">稽首投誠</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">菩提道場</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b03"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">歸依如&CB08074;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">無上三身</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">歸依方廣</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">大乘法藏</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">歸依僧伽</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸菩薩眾</l></lg><p id="pF28p0604b0413" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">三說
<lb ed="F" n="0604b05"/>　念誓受如&CB08074;三歸依戒</note></p><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604b0510">第五翻邪歸正</p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b06"/><lg id="lgF28p0604b0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">弟子某甲等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">歸依佛竟</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">歸依法竟</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">歸依僧竟</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">&CB18813;今<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">巳</rdg></app>往</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">乃至成佛</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">更不歸依</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">二乘外道</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">惟願諸佛</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">慈悲攝受</l></lg><p id="pF28p0604b0905" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">念歸命無盡佛法僧</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b10"/><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604b1001">第六正受菩提心戒</p><lg id="lgF28p0604b1009" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">弟子某甲等</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">仰啟盡十方</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">無量無邊界</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">一切佛菩薩</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">&CB18813;今日<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">巳</rdg></app>往</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">乃至成正覺</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">誓發菩提心</l></lg>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b13"/><lg id="lgF28p0604b1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">有情無邊誓願度</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">福智無邊誓願集</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">佛法無邊誓願學</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">如&CB08074;無邊誓願侍</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">無上菩提誓願成</l></lg><p id="pF28p0604b1508" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">三說　念戒清涼菩薩摩訶薩</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b16"/><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604b1601">第七遣相</p><lg id="lgF28p0604b1605" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">弟子某甲等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">今所發覺心</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b17"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">遠離諸性相</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">蘊處及界等</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">能取所取執</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b18"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸法悉無我</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">平等如虛空</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">自心本不生</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b19"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">空性圓寂故</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">如諸佛菩薩</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">發大菩提心</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b20"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">我亦如是發</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">是故志心禮</l></lg><p id="pF28p0604b2011" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">三說　念遠離一切諸性相</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b21"/><p type="head1" id="pF28p0604b2101">第八普皆迴向</p><lg id="lgF28p0604b2107" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">願以此功德</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">普及於一切</l>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b22"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">我等與眾生</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">皆共成佛道</l></lg><p id="pF28p0604b2211" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">三說　念皆共速成無上覺</note></p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b23"/><p id="pF28p0604b2301">始從此座一剎那<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">間</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">閒</rdg></app>生在佛家終至後身
<lb ed="F" n="0604b24"/>三僧祇內得名佛子此心若在万德咸歸
<lb ed="F" n="0604b25"/>此心若失万德皆喪是故應當善好護持。</p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b26"/><p id="pF28p0604b2601">上&CB08074;普為四眾發菩提心<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">巳</rdg></app>竟齊念摩訶般若。</p>
<lb ed="F" n="0604b27"/><div2 type="w"><p id="pF28p0604b2701" rend="margin-left:1em">石經寺主講經律沙門<note place="inline">志仙</note>&CB09458;統八年十月十五日記</p></div2></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
